  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Brown the lamb on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the onion, garlic, and ginger; cook until the onion is softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin, cinnamon, paprika, salt, and pepper; cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lamb broth, bring to a boil, then cover and transfer to the oven.",
    "Bake at 300°F (150°C) for 2 1/2 hours, or until the lamb is tender.",
    "Stir in the prunes and cook for an additional 10 minutes.",
